# Livotale Development Standards

## Folder Layout

```
src/
├── app/pages/<page>/           # Route pages + page-local components/
├── app/layouts/                # Shell layouts
├── app/routes/                 # Route guards & AppRoutes
├── components/ui/              # shadcn primitives
├── components/common/          # Shared app components (DataTable, Pagination)
├── types/                      # All TypeScript types (@/types)
├── store/                      # Zustand stores (@/store)
├── services/                   # Class-based API services
├── utils/                      # Global utilities (@/utils)
├── hooks/                      # Global hooks
└── rbac/                       # JWT + role access
```

## Page Folderization

Each route page under `src/app/pages/<name>/`:

```
<page>/
├── <Name>Page.tsx      # Page entry (route component)
└── components/         # Page-only UI pieces & small sub-features
```

- Keep page-specific UI in `components/` — not in global `components/`.
- Shared across multiple pages → `src/components/common/` or `src/app/pages/shared/components/`.
- Types → `src/types/<domain>.ts`. Store → `src/store/<domain>/`. Service → `src/services/<domain>/`.

## State Management

- **Zustand** for all shared/async state.
- **Auth, layout**: `src/store/auth/`.
- **Lists/tables**: `createListStore` in `src/store/createListStore.ts`.
- List API calls go through the store — pages never call services directly for list data.

## List / Table Pattern

- **Search**: debounced via `DEBOUNCE.searchMs` (auto-applies in store).
- **Filters**: draft in page components; **Apply Filters** refetches (page resets to 1).
- **Pagination**: debounced via `DEBOUNCE.paginationMs`.
- Use `ListToolbar`, `DataTable`, `PaginationControls` from `@/components/common`.

## Package Manager

Use **pnpm** only.

## Unit Tests

- **Location**: all unit tests live under `tests/`, grouped by feature — never co-located next to source files.
- **Layout** mirrors `src/` domains, e.g. `tests/hooks/`, `tests/utils/`, `tests/components/`, `tests/rbac/`.
- **Naming**: `<module>.test.ts` or `<module>.test.tsx`.
- **Imports**: use `@/` path aliases to reach source modules (e.g. `@/hooks/useUrlTabState`).
- **Only meaningful tests**: skip trivial or obvious behavior; prefer integration-relevant edge cases.
